'''帕克蒂卡省'''（{{lang-fa|د پکتيکا ولايت}}）位於[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]東南方，與[[加茲尼省|加茲尼省]]、[[霍斯特省|霍斯特省]]、[[帕克蒂亞省|帕克蒂亞省]]、[[扎布爾省|扎布爾省]]等省份及[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]相鄰。该省总面积19,482 km²，总人口809,772 (2009) <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nps.edu/Programs/CCS/Docs/Executive%20Summaries/Paktika%20Executive%20Summary%20Final%20Edit.pdf |title=Afghanistan's Provinces Paktika at nps.edu |accessdate=2009-07-28 |archive-date=2009-12-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nps.edu%2FPrograms%2FCCS%2FDocs%2FExecutive%2520Summaries%2FPaktika%2520Executive%2520Summary%2520Final%2520Edit.pdf&date=2009-12-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该省行政中心位于[[沙兰|沙兰]]。

该省辖有19个[[县|县]]。

